Package com.cezar.homework.w03

Class Main

java.lang.Object
com.cezar.homework.w03.Main
public class Main
extends java.lang.Object
Using bubble sort algorithm to sort a list of sales persons based on their revenues. Create a number of instances of SalesRepresentative Class. Each instance represents a sales person. Create a list with those sales representatives. Print the list before and after sorting.
